OL,3,CWindrush generation 'need their
OL,4,Ccompensation' says community leader
OL,6,FA leading Welsh community leader has
OL,7,Fcalled for victims of the to be fully
OL,8,Fcompensated.
OL,10,F, who founded the Windrush Cymru
OL,11,FElders group following the scandal,
OL,12,Fmade the comments to ITV Cymru Wales'
OL,13,FFace To Face programme.
OL,15,FRoma herself arrived in Tiger Bay from
OL,16,FAntigua in 1959, aged just 15.
OL,18,FShe has since become a spokesperson
OL,19,Ffor those who experienced persecution
OL,20,Fand injustice, and recently received a
OL,21,FBritish Empire Medal for her work.
