OL,3,CWindrush generation 'need their
OL,4,Ccompensation' says community leader
OL,6,F"They (the UK Government) need to give
OL,7,Fthe elders, the Windrush Generation,
OL,8,Ftheir compensation," she told Face To
OL,9,FFace.
OL,11,F"There are still people waiting. They
OL,12,Fare old, elderly people, and they need
OL,13,Fto have their compensation."
OL,15,FThe Windrush scandal erupted in 2018
OL,16,Fwhen British citizens, mostly from the
OL,17,FCaribbean, were wrongly detained,
OL,18,Fdeported or threatened with
OL,19,Fdeportation, despite having the right
OL,20,Fto live in Britain.
