OL,6,FMany people lost homes and jobs, and
OL,7,Fwere denied access to healthcare and
OL,8,Fbenefits.
OL,10,FIn 2020, solicitor Wendy Williams
OL,11,Fpublished her 'Windrush Lessons
OL,12,FLearned Review', and all 30 of her
OL,13,Frecommendations were originally
OL,14,Faccepted by then-home secretary Priti
OL,15,FPatel.
