OL,3,CWindrush generation 'need their
OL,4,Ccompensation' says community leader
OL,6,FHowever, in January 2023 it was
OL,7,Fconfirmed that Suella Braverman, who
OL,8,Fwas in post as home secretary by that
OL,9,Fstage, had dropped three commitments,
OL,10,Fincluding establishing a migrants'
OL,11,Fcommissioner, increasing the powers of
OL,12,Fthe independent chief inspector of
OL,13,Fborders and immigration, and to hold
OL,14,Freconciliation events.
OL,16,FCampaigners have previously described
OL,17,Fthe axing of these recommendations as
OL,18,Fa "kick in the teeth", and campaigners
OL,19,Fsuch as Welsh athlete Colin Jackson
OL,20,Fhave described the progress as
OL,21,F"painfully slow".
