OL,3,CWindrush generation 'need their
OL,4,Ccompensation' says community leader
OL,6,F"There's a lot more (that) needs to be
OL,7,Fdone," Roma continued. "It's started,
OL,8,Fbut more has to be done, especially
OL,9,Feverything that has to do with racism."
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the UK Government's
OL,12,FHome Office said: "Five years on, our
OL,13,Fdetermination to right the wrongs of
OL,14,Fthe Windrush scandal remains as strong
OL,15,Fas ever and we have paid out more than
OL,16,F#75 million in compensation.
OL,18,F"We have also made significant
OL,19,Fprogress since Wendy Williams' review
OL,20,Fand our important work to implement
OL,21,Fher recommendations continues.
